BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 123.84 600 Td (Chapter 1: What is Etsy?) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Etsy is an online marketplace focused on handmade, vintage, and craft items.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Founded in 2005, it now has over 90 million active buyers worldwide.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Unlike Amazon, Etsy shoppers specifically seek unique and creative products.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (You can sell physical goods, digital downloads, or vintage items over 20 years old.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Popular categories include jewelry, home decor, art prints, and personalized gifts.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Etsy charges a small listing fee of $0.20 per item plus a transaction fee.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (The platform handles payments so you do not need your own payment processor.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Many sellers start as a side hustle and grow into full-time businesses.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (You do not need a business license to start but check your local laws.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Etsy provides built-in traffic so you do not need to build your own website.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Millions of people earn a living selling on Etsy from their homes.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (This book will guide you from zero to your first sale step by step.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (1) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
