BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 85.44 600 Td (Chapter 2: Setting Up Your Account) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Go to etsy.com and click the Sell on Etsy button to begin registration.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (You will need a valid email address, your name, and your country.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Choose your shop language and currency based on your target market.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Etsy will ask you to name your shop which must be unique on the platform.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Your shop name should be memorable, easy to spell, and reflect your brand.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Avoid numbers and special characters that make your name hard to remember.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Set up your payment method to receive funds via direct deposit or PayPal.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Add a billing method so Etsy can charge listing and transaction fees.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Complete your shop profile with a photo and a compelling bio about yourself.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Write your shop announcement to greet visitors and explain what you sell.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Set your shop policies including shipping times, returns, and exchanges.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Verify your identity if prompted to build trust with potential buyers.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (2) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
