BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 112.32000000000001 600 Td (Chapter 3: Choosing a Niche) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (A niche is a specific category of products you specialize in selling.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Successful Etsy shops focus on one area rather than selling everything.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Research trending niches by browsing Etsy bestsellers and social media.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Consider your skills, hobbies, and passions when choosing your niche.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Look for niches with demand but not overwhelming competition.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Digital products like printables and templates have zero shipping costs.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Personalized items like custom name jewelry consistently sell well.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Wedding items have high demand and buyers willing to pay premium prices.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Pet products are a growing niche with passionate buyers.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Use Etsy search to see how many results appear for your product ideas.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Check if top sellers in your niche have many sales proving demand exists.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Start narrow and expand later once you understand your customers.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (3) Tj ET

endstream
