BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 81.6 600 Td (Chapter 4: Product Photography Tips) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Great photos are the number one factor in getting Etsy sales.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Use natural light by photographing near a large window during daytime.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (A white poster board makes an affordable clean background for products.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Take photos from multiple angles: front, back, side, and detail shots.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Include a photo showing scale so buyers understand the actual size.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Lifestyle photos showing your product in use dramatically increase sales.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Use your smartphone camera which is perfectly adequate for Etsy photos.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Keep backgrounds clean and uncluttered so the product is the focus.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Edit photos for brightness and contrast using free apps like Snapseed.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Etsy allows up to 10 photos per listing so use all available slots.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Your first photo is the thumbnail shoppers see in search results.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Consistent photo style across listings makes your shop look professional.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (4) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
