BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 73.92000000000002 600 Td (Chapter 5: Writing Listings That Sell) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Your listing title should include keywords buyers actually search for.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Front-load the most important keywords at the beginning of your title.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Write descriptions that answer every question a buyer might have.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Include dimensions, materials, colors, and care instructions clearly.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Use bullet points or short paragraphs so descriptions are easy to scan.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Tell a story about your product to create an emotional connection.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Mention the problem your product solves or the joy it brings.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Include information about customization options and how to request them.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Address common concerns like shipping time and packaging in descriptions.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Use all 13 keyword tags Etsy gives you for each listing.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Update listings regularly as Etsy favors recently refreshed content.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Study bestselling competitors to learn what their descriptions include.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (5) Tj ET

endstream
