BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 93.12 600 Td (Chapter 6: Pricing Your Products) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Many new sellers underprice their work which leads to burnout and failure.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Calculate your costs: materials, packaging, shipping supplies, and Etsy fees.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Add your time at a fair hourly rate even if this is a hobby.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (The basic formula is: materials plus labor plus overhead times two.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Research what competitors charge for similar items in your niche.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Factor in Etsy fees: listing fee, transaction fee, and payment processing.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Free shipping often increases sales so consider building it into your price.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Offer multiple price points with basic and premium versions of products.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Do not compete solely on price as this is a race to the bottom.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Raise prices gradually as you gain reviews and establish your brand.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Test different price points to find what converts best for your items.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Remember that buyers on Etsy expect to pay more for handmade quality.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (6) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
