BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 116.16 600 Td (Chapter 7: Shipping Basics) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Choose between flat rate shipping and calculated shipping by weight.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (USPS, UPS, and FedEx all offer competitive rates for small packages.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Etsy provides discounted shipping labels you can print at home.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Invest in a small postal scale to weigh packages accurately.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Stock up on shipping supplies: boxes, mailers, bubble wrap, and tape.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Set realistic processing times you can consistently meet.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Always add tracking numbers so both you and buyers can follow packages.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Consider offering free shipping on orders over a certain amount.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (International shipping opens your market but adds complexity and cost.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Package items securely with extra protection for fragile products.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Include a thank you note or small freebie to delight your customers.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Ship on time or early to build a reputation for reliability.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (7) Tj ET

