BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 108.48 600 Td (Chapter 8: Etsy SEO Keywords) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (SEO means Search Engine Optimization and helps buyers find your listings.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Etsy search works differently from Google so learn its specific rules.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Use long-tail keywords that describe exactly what your product is.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Think like a buyer: what words would they type to find your item?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Use all 13 tags per listing and make each one a unique phrase.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Your title, tags, categories, and attributes all affect search ranking.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Etsy also considers listing quality score based on clicks and purchases.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Renew listings strategically as freshly renewed items get a temporary boost.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Use Etsy search bar suggestions to discover what people are searching.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Tools like eRank and Marmalead help you research keyword competition.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Avoid single-word tags as they are too broad and competitive.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Update your keywords seasonally to capture holiday and trending searches.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (8) Tj ET

