BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 93.12 600 Td (Chapter 9: Customer Service Tips) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Respond to all messages within 24 hours to maintain your response rate.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Be friendly, professional, and helpful even with difficult customers.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Answer questions thoroughly to prevent misunderstandings before purchase.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Set clear expectations in your listings to reduce customer service issues.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Handle complaints gracefully as one bad review can hurt your shop.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Offer solutions like replacements or refunds when problems arise.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Follow up after delivery to ensure customers are satisfied.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (A five-star review is worth more than any single sale in the long run.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Create FAQ sections in your listings for common questions.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Personalize your communication so customers feel valued and special.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Use saved replies for common questions to save time without losing quality.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Happy customers become repeat buyers and recommend you to friends.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (9) Tj ET

