BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 77.75999999999999 600 Td (Chapter 13: Common Mistakes to Avoid) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Do not open your shop with only one or two listings. Aim for at least 20.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Avoid copying other sellers as Etsy can suspend shops for infringement.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Do not use trademarked terms or characters without proper licensing.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Never ignore customer messages as this hurts your shop ranking.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Avoid underpricing your products just to make quick sales.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Do not skip product photography and use stock images instead.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Avoid generic titles and descriptions that do not include keywords.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Do not give up after one month. Most shops take 3-6 months to gain traction.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Never buy fake reviews as Etsy will permanently ban your shop.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Avoid overpromising on shipping times you cannot consistently meet.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Do not neglect your shop after initial setup. Regular updates matter.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Avoid trying to sell everything. Focus on your niche and do it well.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 211.2 30 Td (13) Tj ET

