BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 58.56 600 Td (Chapter 14: Legal Basics \(Taxes/Licenses\)) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Check your local city and state requirements for business licenses.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (A sole proprietorship is the simplest business structure to start with.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (You may need a sales tax permit depending on your state.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Report all Etsy income on your tax return even if you do not get a 1099.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Home business deductions can include a portion of rent and utilities.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Keep records of all business expenses for at least seven years.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Consider liability insurance especially if you sell consumable products.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Understand intellectual property laws to protect your designs.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Trademark your brand name if you plan to grow significantly.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Consult a local small business development center for free guidance.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Many cities have free workshops for new entrepreneurs on legal basics.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Start simple and add legal protections as your business grows.) Tj ET
