BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 85.44 600 Td (Chapter 15: Your First 30-Day Plan) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Days 1-3: Research your niche and study successful shops in that category.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Days 4-5: Set up your Etsy account and complete all shop profile sections.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Days 6-10: Create your first 10 products or designs for your shop.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Days 11-13: Photograph all products with multiple angles and good lighting.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Days 14-16: Write compelling listings with keyword-rich titles and descriptions.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Days 17-18: Set up shipping profiles and pricing for all your items.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Day 19: Publish all listings and make your shop officially open.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Days 20-22: Set up social media accounts \(Pinterest and Instagram minimum\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Days 23-25: Create and post content driving traffic to your Etsy shop.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Days 26-28: Add 5-10 more listings. More listings means more visibility.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Days 29-30: Review analytics, adjust keywords, and plan next month.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Celebrate your progress! Most people never take the first step at all.) Tj ET
